title: OnePlus 10 Pro kernel source code is now available
content:
OnePlus finally took the wraps off the global variant of the OnePlus 10 Pro, but the company slacked off a bit and did not give us the kernel sources right after the launch. If you have already managed to score one for yourself for the sake of tinkering, we have good news for you. To

The post OnePlus 10 Pro kernel source code is now available appeared first on xda-developers.
description: OnePlus has finally released the kernel sources for the OnePlus 10 Pro, kickstarting third-party development for its latest flagship.
